## Prerequisites

- Python 3.12+
- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) (Python package manager)
- Docker and Docker Compose

## Local Development

### Quick Start

```bash
make start
```

This starts the full stack (PostgreSQL, Redis, FastAPI) via Docker Compose.

The API will be available at http://localhost:8000 with interactive docs at http://localhost:8000/docs.

### Common Commands

```bash
make start       # Start all services
make stop        # Stop all services
make logs        # Follow all service logs
make bash        # Shell into the web container
make shell       # Python interactive shell
make test        # Run test suite
make migrate     # Run Alembic migrations
make migration   # Create new Alembic migration
make reqs        # Compile requirements files
```

### Manual Setup (without Docker)

```bash
uv venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
uv pip compile requirements.in -o requirements.txt
uv pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env  # Edit with your settings
alembic upgrade head
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

